Privacy Policy for Rizqi - Customer App
Last Updated: March 29, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes how Rizqi (Customer) ("we," "our," or "the App") collects, uses, and shares information about users looking for professional and construction services in Iraq. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

1. Information Collection and Use
To provide a seamless experience in finding and hiring service providers, we collect the following:

Account Information: When you sign in via Google or WhatsApp, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and profile picture.

Location Data: We collect your precise or approximate location (GPS) to show you nearby service providers (Engineers, Technicians, etc.) on the map and calculate the distance to them.

Interaction Data: We collect data regarding your service requests, provider ratings, and reviews to maintain the quality of our marketplace.

Device Information: We collect technical data such as device model, OS version, and app performance logs to ensure a smooth user experience.

2. How We Use Your Data
We use the collected data for the following purposes:

Service Matching: To connect you with available providers within a 20km radius.

Communication: To facilitate the in-app chat system between you and the service provider once a request is initiated.

Personalization: To suggest categories and featured providers based on your location and past interests.

Security: To prevent fraudulent activity and ensure a safe environment for both customers and providers.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
With Providers: When you request a service, your name and location are shared with the provider to facilitate the job. Your phone number is only shared via the secure chat or upon confirmation.

Third-Party Services: We use trusted services like Firebase (for database and authentication), Google AdMob (for relevant ads), and OpenStreetMap (for mapping services). These parties have their own privacy policies.

Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities in Iraq.

4. Data Storage and Security
Your data is stored securely using Firebase Cloud Firestore.

All data transmissions are encrypted using HTTPS/TLS protocols.

We use strict Firebase Security Rules to ensure that your personal information is only accessible by you and authorized system processes.

5. Your Rights and Data Deletion
Access and Correction: You can update your profile information directly within the App settings.

Account Deletion: You have the right to delete your account and all associated personal data at any time. Upon deletion, your profile, request history, and identifiers will be permanently removed from our active databases.

6. Children's Privacy
Our services are not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

